{"tid":2430653,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"找12-15歲學生填問卷（5名幸運兒每人獲得港幣$100元＋中文DSE實戰5星星作文）","createTime":"2021-03-03T05:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T09:29:42.000Z","uid":393299,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2e333604ae1b86a75b530872dd7bb9b653c17ffa","tid":2430653,"uid":393299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:39:24.000Z","msg":"【隨機抽取5名幸運兒每人獲得港幣$100元💵💵💵💵💵】<br />\n【完成問卷可提供中文DSE實戰5⭐⭐作文】<br />\n您好，我是香港中文大學心理學系學生，現正進行「父母管教如何影響學業成績」的研究，招募年齡介乎12至15歲的香港學生完成十分鐘的問卷🙏🏻。由於是次研究的sample size 不大，所以中獎機率大為提高。<br />\n<br />\n【參加者要求】<br />\n- 年齡介乎12至15歲的香港學生<br />\n- 具備基本閱讀中文的能力<br />\n- 與父母同住<br />\n<br />\n【研究流程】<br />\n1. 點擊以下連結，完成家長授權。<br />\n<a href=\"http://esurvey.psy.cuhk.edu.hk/jfe/form/SV_71yOy2pp889jA3P\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fesurvey.psy.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_71yOy2pp889jA3P&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=c22bb952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://esurvey.psy.cuhk.edu.hk/jfe/form/SV_71yOy2pp889jA3P</a><br />\n2. 讓子女繼續填妥問卷。<br />\n3. 等待抽獎結果，將透過電郵通知。<br />\n<br />\n如您對本研究計劃有任何疑問，歡迎電郵至1155108781@link.cuhk.edu.hk與本計劃的研究員聯絡。謝謝🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️！"},{"pid":"ff69826a4d53aa792643f1551763052cdcd29138","tid":2430653,"uid":336670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"d81306c9eb00bf4d5bc757a3e8fd73298e534d2e","tid":2430653,"uid":201414,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:52:05.000Z","msg":"托咩 100蚊 我係班細佬正值青春期寧願要J圖打下丁好過"},{"pid":"c578080725b683acba8194cc39d61b49c10b9862","tid":2430653,"uid":56550,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"隨機抽取5名<br />\n屌你老母on99<br />\n要幅J圖好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3cc7d5c17115e59c34bf1167e7fab45acbf0346","tid":2430653,"uid":118502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"完成問卷可提供中文DSE實戰5⭐⭐作文 <br />\n你直接送呢樣野比人好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5942fbf55292db425906cb667a65e59bc0cef38","tid":2430653,"uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:03:56.000Z","msg":"度縮到咁縮翻入老母個閪到啦"},{"pid":"3e1798bf3f97947a47a82c137e6f5618bf6ba1f9","tid":2430653,"uid":38098,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:07:08.000Z","msg":"唔知你有無拎抽獎牌照<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你有齊學校email等民政署嚟問下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5cd5dd6fe1b78edad4665a2d53c4bea1cefc09","tid":2430653,"uid":367147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:14:46.000Z","msg":"po去babycondom啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437821864472f545daf306becb93f2bd15d03b64","tid":2430653,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我廿歲扮15歲先"},{"pid":"8d86a77ba8342d3fd55cd0c34b8bfd0fa3f748a1","tid":2430653,"uid":393530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5dc9ae70a8cca6ef225625d5d4d0dfafea62c02e","tid":2430653,"uid":393530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:29:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}